a\"<br/><small>(featuring Sauti Sol)</small>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Tumbum\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Knack Am\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| rowspan=\"5\"| ''Black Magic''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Single and Searching\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Heart Robber\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bum Bum\"\n| rowspan=\"5\"| 2018\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Kpirim\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Oh My Gosh\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" {{N/A|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Oga\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"How I Feel\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Bounce\"\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2019\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Home\"\n| rowspan=\"6\" |''Woman of Steel''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Give Dem\" <br/><small>(featuring [[Duncan Mighty]])</small>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Vibe\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Shake\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Remind You\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|2020\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Shekere\" <br/><small>(featuring [[Ang\u00e9lique Kidjo]])</small>\n|}\n\n=== Promotional singles ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Classic Girl Freestyle\"<br/><small>([[Jidenna]]'s \"[[Classic Man]]\" cover)</small>\n| 2015\n| rowspan=\"9\" {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Koffi Anan (Freestyle)\"<ref>{{cite web|title=New Music Yemi Alade \u2013 'Koffi Anan' (Freestyle)|url=http://pulse.ng/new_music/new-music-yemi-alade-koffi-anan-freestyle-id4597767.html|website=Pulse.ng|publisher=Amaka Inyese|accessdate=25 January 2016}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Want You\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Get Through This\"<br/><small>(featuring Mi Casa)</small>\n| 2017\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bum Bum\"\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2018\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Issokay\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"How I Feel\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Oh My Gosh\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bounce\"\n|2019\n|-\n|}\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n\n=== [[All Africa Music Awards|AFR